{"id": "ChIJxWoYt7zpj4ARNu5jI8Ad_to", "rating": 4.8, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 4358, "displayName": {"text": "Meadowlark Dairy", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Long-running drive-through offering milk, cheese, ice cream & other dairy products, plus fast fare.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJxWoYt7zpj4ARNu5jI8Ad_to/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xZeGJscFNTWHB6UkRONFpGVkJVV0pWWldKbWFsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Awesome ice cream.  Line wraps around the block but it moves very fast.  Some of the best soft serve I have ever had.  Totally worth the wait.  The staff is full of energy and does a great job helping you decide.  The whole area has a nice vibe to it.  I had the chocolate which was great.  The mango was even better that my wife had.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Awesome ice cream.  Line wraps around the block but it moves very fast.  Some of the best soft serve I have ever had.  Totally worth the wait.  The staff is full of energy and does a great job helping you decide.  The whole area has a nice vibe to it.  I had the chocolate which was great.  The mango was even better that my wife had.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "S Mir", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100850685938018924903/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxdP0BqKODda9G0JMal2olQqa7WSad4k3xmZ0mAYqO59PTcQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-05T06:24:13.179310688Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xZeGJscFNTWHB6UkRONFpGVkJVV0pWWldKbWFsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xZeGJscFNTWHB6UkRONFpGVkJVV0pWWldKbWFsRRAB!2m1!1s0x808fe9bcb7186ac5:0xdafe1dc02363ee36"}, {"name": "places/ChIJxWoYt7zpj4ARNu5jI8Ad_to/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaWWMycERUVUZ1UnpSTk1sTm5WVVJKZGpNelVWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a week ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This is probably one of the best soft serve I had it in long time. They also have vegan options. It did look good but didn't try. The classic vanilla chocolate did hit the spot and did not disappoint after the long drive we took to try this! Grab the soft serve, cross the road and enjoy it in the garden nearby!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is probably one of the best soft serve I had it in long time. They also have vegan options. It did look good but didn't try. The classic vanilla chocolate did hit the spot and did not disappoint after the long drive we took to try this! Grab the soft serve, cross the road and enjoy it in the garden nearby!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Pranjali Naik", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103001422901142855320/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBfsT9a-GWqHgvTWL4UHwUcarUKtuMWFbHA9jjOSTRcWgGCS0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-07-07T00:26:56.326391280Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaWWMycERUVUZ1UnpSTk1sTm5WVVJKZGpNelVWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaWWMycERUVUZ1UnpSTk1sTm5WVVJKZGpNelVWRRAB!2m1!1s0x808fe9bcb7186ac5:0xdafe1dc02363ee36"}, {"name": "places/ChIJxWoYt7zpj4ARNu5jI8Ad_to/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21ST2FIZGZVMUJ6YjFOQ1ZEVlFjMk5CYW5CaFYyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Delicious ice cream..dont be scared when you see the drive thru line, they bust out the icecream super fast..super incredible how they stack the flavors. Any flavor can be swirled with vanilla, but if you dont get vanilla, they \"stack\" the flavors. Really nice workers too.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Delicious ice cream..dont be scared when you see the drive thru line, they bust out the icecream super fast..super incredible how they stack the flavors. Any flavor can be swirled with vanilla, but if you dont get vanilla, they \"stack\" the flavors. Really nice workers too.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jill Dalemar", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112309771303669544212/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKk_vF1h-wBHSvk9J4H2OFrEcV0GKphNYNfLhrk6uGlJUH6Cg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-16T11:28:27.750772635Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21ST2FIZGZVMUJ6YjFOQ1ZEVlFjMk5CYW5CaFYyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21ST2FIZGZVMUJ6YjFOQ1ZEVlFjMk5CYW5CaFYyYxAB!2m1!1s0x808fe9bcb7186ac5:0xdafe1dc02363ee36"}, {"name": "places/ChIJxWoYt7zpj4ARNu5jI8Ad_to/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GNVpFdEdTM2hmVWsxQllTMUtiUzFQVUZsekxXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Tried the vanilla blueberry and vanilla chocolate soft-serve, and both were great! The drive-thru experience is incredibly smooth and efficient. I'll definitely try different flavors when I go back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Tried the vanilla blueberry and vanilla chocolate soft-serve, and both were great! The drive-thru experience is incredibly smooth and efficient. I'll definitely try different flavors when I go back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tarun", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100604507397848630712/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyuBVrIwBy3-3fRdfbSVJx6H4xTWw-kr_gUqsKjrz_bqf9llk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-07T04:42:33.206737121Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GNVpFdEdTM2hmVWsxQllTMUtiUzFQVUZsekxXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GNVpFdEdTM2hmVWsxQllTMUtiUzFQVUZsekxXYxAB!2m1!1s0x808fe9bcb7186ac5:0xdafe1dc02363ee36"}, {"name": "places/ChIJxWoYt7zpj4ARNu5jI8Ad_to/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WVVVXcHRXbWxGWlU1c1ExaDJWWFV5T0VsMlEwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I came through from a recommendation from local family who said this spot is historic and a must visit when in Pleasanton. They weren’t kidding. It was a pretty nippy day and while there weren’t many folks in the counter line, there were tons of cars lining up around the corner for the drive-thru. I opted for the classic chocolate and vanilla swirl, medium size and boy oh boy, what a deal. This thing was huge for a medium and costing only $3.50? This is an unbelievably good deal. It almost felt like stealing. The ice cream was so thick and rich. The first bite coated my mouth with some high quality cow juice. I could tell this was some good stuff and I am still shocked at how affordable the cone is. Apparently I came at a good time because after I ordered, there were about three dozen people behind me. It really does seem like ice cream tastes better when the weather is colder. It melts slower too, but I didn’t have trouble getting this cone down. This was a super yummy one for the books. Looking forward to coming back to try the other flavors.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I came through from a recommendation from local family who said this spot is historic and a must visit when in Pleasanton. They weren’t kidding. It was a pretty nippy day and while there weren’t many folks in the counter line, there were tons of cars lining up around the corner for the drive-thru. I opted for the classic chocolate and vanilla swirl, medium size and boy oh boy, what a deal. This thing was huge for a medium and costing only $3.50? This is an unbelievably good deal. It almost felt like stealing. The ice cream was so thick and rich. The first bite coated my mouth with some high quality cow juice. I could tell this was some good stuff and I am still shocked at how affordable the cone is. Apparently I came at a good time because after I ordered, there were about three dozen people behind me. It really does seem like ice cream tastes better when the weather is colder. It melts slower too, but I didn’t have trouble getting this cone down. This was a super yummy one for the books. Looking forward to coming back to try the other flavors.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Frank Biermann", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110467863817034275907/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqB-s8Ol9yQLenaFJojUyJlhi0xqIwez4DkvmpmI1VC0f9cu0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-21T23:30:01.666711828Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WVVVXcHRXbWxGWlU1c1ExaDJWWFV5T0VsMlEwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WVVVXcHRXbWxGWlU1c1ExaDJWWFV5T0VsMlEwRRAB!2m1!1s0x808fe9bcb7186ac5:0xdafe1dc02363ee36"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJxWoYt7zpj4ARNu5jI8Ad_to/photos/AWCwydgnNhbTyQX8gmcBKU9CiKPKinALFSIElf90eoDMUX8r6saemJ6Z9QSrkDg3HJs-0G8wLPQNPV4wpiKVjSimSvfk499ECYenl_L8hSTwZry051GVAWHsbacnJP__gel1wdD4OLlQRJHx8xzRFKXQA8lp1LeyiwDH6L7Z2XL6e7yNTHDZGqFnlI4Sobmc3B2rxcmSqzu1UFcrUrdme2NyH2-C9BbfHYB0YVGzwwbc0Bq13ZruE2Mj-OOyYpSCH8acYVZ6BDPfDhbshSPiJSTmA_r92xhE0EDqwWbXa9t3aabMzVrIfOw9pdiEtnbpbHnj07M17wYC-Sxh918DVO2qRxiC7QbAL1fv7V9uqplQpuR8VCH_ByJNM-67uxRvYVZUWHmE2zcPMU5ApEU3sJQDGEwUoR7_SI4MkO7RopUXKBO3DQ", "widthPx": 2048, "heightPx": 1152